This object is generated for Raspberry Pi ARM64 by the top-level Makefile.

Build the Rust core with:

    make rust-core

Equivalent Cargo target:

    cargo +nightly build -Zbuild-std=core,alloc \
        --target aarch64-unknown-none --release

Do not copy a prebuilt x86_64 object into this directory. The generated
object must be AArch64 ELF and must be linked against the exact Raspberry Pi
kernel build tree used by the final stcp.ko module.
